              <span id="reviewTextContainer614130320" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8045199549209189568">What a great story for a first time author. Science fiction is not my chosen genre to read and I found myself absorbed in the story to the end. There are a number of typing errors still evident and a few errors with colloquial speech but these do not detract from the story. The suspense is held right up to the end of the book which keeps the reader engaged. <br/></span>

          </span>
        </div>


